dct_title_s: New Milford, Bergen County, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: "August 1930." Includes location map, key, streets and specials index, and text. "4929." North oriented towards upper left. Historic Maps copy includes sheets 1, 6-7 and 9 of New Milford, N.J. series; sheets 2-5, showing Peetzburg section, sheet 8, showing River Edge Manor section, and sheet 10, showing New Bridge section, foldered separately.
